about.mission.text:
Our mission is two-fold; we want the daily lives of our landlords and tenants to  become easier and much more enjoyable by building a platform supporting laundry facilities  and also the communication between landlords and tenants.  {nl}
  {nl}
  We also want to improve the environment by encoring more people to share their laundry  facilities while nudging people to wash at times during the day that are more environmentally  friendly by analysing anonymized data collected from our users.

